content.rendered: Cheekbone fillers are incredibly popular due to their ability to improve the face’s shape. They can be very beneficial for people who have lost volume to the middle of their cheeks due to aging or weight loss, and they can help provide added support to other sagging parts of the face. We use high density HA filler injections to highlight and sharpen the cheekbones, ‘’fill’’ the empty parts and rebuild the contouring of the face creating a more youthful ,refreshed look.
